name: Kane Mayfield - A Year & A Day

metadata.name: Identity (A Year & A Day)
metadata.description:
One year (and a day) ago I minted my very first NFT.

I wrote a letter to be included in the unlockable content and it was just such a crazy and rewarding ride from then till now.

I made this (quite different) version of it to commemorate the year and a day I've spent as an NFT artist.

Thank you all for taking the time to read this, also if you didn't take the time to read this I can technically put whatever I want in here. Your mom has a wooden leg... big schwams and fondue. This is way too much responsibility for someone like me. Im gonna start sending my descriptions to Fiverr.
